---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/main.astro";
import Arrow from "../components/svg/arrow.svelte";
---

<MainLayout title="Control Panel">
  <section transition:animate="slide">
    <div
      class="grid h-[50rem] grid-rows-4 bg-gray-200 px-5 py-12 lg:grid-cols-2 xl:px-16 2xl:px-20"
    >
      <p
        class="line-clamp-1 text-center text-5xl font-medium tracking-widest text-stone-700 sm:text-6xl lg:col-start-1 lg:col-end-2 lg:row-start-1 lg:row-end-2"
      >
        Control Panel
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-justify text-2xl tracking-wide text-stone-700 sm:text-4xl lg:col-start-2 lg:col-end-3 lg:row-start-2 lg:row-end-3"
      >
        Control Panel is a project intended to assist in the management of
        appointments.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-justify text-2xl tracking-wide text-stone-700 sm:text-4xl lg:col-start-2 lg:col-end-3 lg:row-start-3 lg:row-end-4"
      >
        You can verify, add, reschedule and cancel appointments based on the
        odontologist's schedule.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-justify text-2xl tracking-wide text-stone-700 sm:text-4xl lg:col-start-2 lg:col-end-3 lg:row-start-4 lg:row-end-5"
      >
        All appointments are verified, meaning that you do not have to worry
        about appointments overlapping.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="h-[50rem] bg-gradient-to-b from-teal-500 to-emerald-500"></div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
